FT  14 JUN 94 / UK Company News: Trinity contract
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Mr Geoff Hollyhead, chairman of Trinity Holdings, told the annual meeting
that the vehicle manufacturer had been awarded a contract to supply
Badgerline with 576 bus chassis.
Together with further orders, including 160 chassis for Stagecoach, the
contract constituted a record monthly intake for the Dennis Specialist
Vehicles subsidiary, totalling some Pounds 33m.
This latest contract pushed Trinity's order book for the current year to
some Pounds 100m.
