FT  14 JUN 94 / UK Company News: Cheltenham &amp; Gloucester faces legal action
from former partner
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Cannon Assurance, an offshoot of Lincoln National, the US life assurance
group, is taking legal action against the Cheltenham &amp; Gloucester Building
Society claiming it has not been paid fees for introducing mortgage
customers.
